---
// WorkProcessSection.astro
---
<section class="my-16">
  <div class="text-center mb-10">
    <p class="text-blue-600 font-semibold text-lg mb-2">Sustainable, Reliable & Affordable Energy!</p>
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800">Our Work Process</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 h-full">
      <div class="text-green-600 mb-4">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-14 h-14" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 1.343-3 3 0 1.657 1.343 3 3 3s3-1.343 3-3c0-1.657-1.343-3-3-3zm0 0V4m0 0C7.582 4 4 7.582 4 12c0 4.418 3.582 8 8 8s8-3.582 8-8c0-4.418-3.582-8-8-8z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Environmental Responsibility</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">We prioritize eco-friendly practices, minimizing the environmental impact of our projects.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 h-full">
      <div class="text-blue-600 mb-4">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-14 h-14" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Maintenance and Support</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">Post-completion, we offer ongoing maintenance and support services, ensuring the long-term performance of our EHV power transmission lines.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 h-full">
      <div class="text-red-600 mb-4">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-14 h-14" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01M21 12c0 4.97-4.03 9-9 9s-9-4.03-9-9 4.03-9 9-9 9 4.03 9 9z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Safety & Commitment</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">Safety is our top priority, and we adhere to strict safety protocols to protect our team and the communities where we work.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg p-8 h-full">
      <div class="text-emerald-600 mb-4">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="w-14 h-14" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m4 0h-1v-4h-1m-4 0h-1v-4h-1m4 0h-1v-4h-1"/></svg>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Innovation and Sustainability</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-600">We continually explore innovative solutions and sustainable practices to contribute to a greener and more reliable energy future.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
